org.openadaptor.core.router
Class Autoboxer

java.lang.Object
  org.openadaptor.core.router.Autoboxer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAutoboxer
public class Autoboxer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAutoboxer

Implementation of IAutoboxer that wraps the following

  • IReadConnector
  • IDataProcessor
  • IWriteConnector
    as
  • ReadNode
  • ProcessorNode
  • WriteNode
    respectively. Also wraps single values as unary element lists and various other things that allow users to simplify the configuration of an IRoutingMap.
